import { Paper, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow } from "@mui/material" import axios from "axios" import { useEffect, useState } from "react" import IRestaurante from "../../../interfaces/IRestaurante" const AdministracaoRestaurantes = () => { const [restaurantes, setRestaurantes] = useState([]) useEffect(()=>{ axios.get('http://localhost:8000/api/v2/restaurantes/') .then(resposta => setRestaurantes(resposta.data)) },[]) return ( nome Editar {restaurantes.map(restaurante => {restaurante.nome} )}
) } export default AdministracaoRestaurantes
